name: My Cat - Attract wealth
description:
Have you been dreaming of getting a pet for a long time? I'm telling you, now you can own a cat right now ! Take care of all cute cats here and start enjoying your day!

Game features of My Cat:
-Merge & Idle & Development
-Unlock cats to win game rewards
-Collection of cats with different meanings

Different cats represent different wishes,expressing the everlasting hope of human beings for happiness,contentment,and good luck.Come and explore the secrets of cats!

Is this adorable？Download and own a cat now！
